text: John Daniel Caine (born August 10, 1968) is an American Air Force general and venture capitalist. He has been the 22nd chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff since 2025. He was the associate director for military affairs at the Central Intelligence Agency from 2021 to 2024. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Chairmen of the Joint Chiefs of Staff Category:Military people from New York (state) Category:American generals
